    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Seems a bit of a pointless requirement in a world where clock skew is a thing.  Beacon nodes cannot rely on blocks not arriving late, and validator clients are already incentivized to produce a block as quickly as possible.",
